abstract: BELVIDERE, N.J., May 8.--Nellie Hooper, the 14-year-old daughter of Prof. Hooper, of Belvidere Academy, was kidnapped by her mother at Phillipsburg Saturday afternoon and taken to Atlantic City. The town is considerably excited over the affair.

abstract: NEWBURG, N.Y., May 28.--The representatives of the Synod of the Reformed Presbyterian Church of America will convene in this city, in Westminster Church, on Wednesday, June 1.
